{
  "text": "In two dimensions, it is not hard to show that uniform ellipticity implies the Cordes condition (2.2) with \u03b5 = 2\u03bd/(\u03bd +\u03bd), see [CITATION_1] . Define the strictly positive function \u03b3 \u2208 L \u221e (\u2126) by",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "3643732"
